snippet: President Viktor F. Yanukovich signaled Thursday that former Prime Minister Yulia V. Tymoshenko could be released from prison and sent to Germany to get treated for a back problem.
abstract: Ukraine's Pres Viktor F Yanukovich says his main rival, former Prime Min Yulia V Tymoshenko, could be released from prison and sent to Germany to get treated for a back problem; European Union has refused to sign an integration agreement with Ukraine as long as Tymoshenko remains in jail, which West condemns as politically motivated.
lead_paragraph: President Viktor F. Yanukovich signaled Thursday that former Prime Minister Yulia V. Tymoshenko could be released from prison and sent to Germany to get treated for a back problem.
